+
+**Action:** Review fix-pass polish for the Claude tmux ready detector and script packaging. `CLAUDE_READY_FOOTER_MARKER` is now `← for agents` (status-footer shape) so a busy line that merely mentions "for agents" is not treated as chrome; rejection fixture covers that case. `WRAPPER_SCRIPT` is pinned via `WRAPPER_SCRIPT_BASENAME` rather than `REFERENCED_SCRIPT_BASENAMES.fetch(0)`. Built-gem package test asserts every on-disk `lib/hive/scripts/**/*.sh` is present in the artifact (closes residual stop_hook packaging hole if the gemspec glob narrows later).
+
+**Tags:** #architecture
